scene.message:
Tadashi: ...It's okay.{nl}
No matter what, I'll{nl}
protect you.{waitkey}{clearbox}So...{wait_fr:30} so believe in me{nl}
and follow me, Tamaki!{nl}
I love you!!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: We always just{nl}
fought... but that was{nl}
because I worried about you.{waitkey}{clearbox}You never knew how I felt...{nl}
Leave you alone and you{nl}
always do reckless things.{waitkey}{clearbox}But thanks to that dream,{nl}
I can finally be honest...{nl}
Tadashi...{wait_fr:30} I love you!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Oh-ho, at it again.{nl}
They never get tired{nl}
of it.{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, all three are awake{nl}
and safe now.{nl}
You all feeling okay?{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Ahh! Ahh!{nl}
It was just getting good!!{nl}
Don't interrupt!{waitkey}{clearbox}Right, Tamaki?{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: ...Mayuzumi,{nl}
everyone... why are{nl}
you here?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: You remember nothing?{nl}
What blissfully ignorant{nl}
fools.{waitkey}{clearbox}A waste of time, a thankless{nl}
rescue, exactly. I'm too{nl}
dumbfounded to speak.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Ehh! Come on,{nl}
so cold, Tamaki.{nl}
After I worked so hard{waitkey}to save you!{waitkey}{clearbox}You don't remember a thing?{nl}
That's a bit much, no?{nl}
I'm super sad here.{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Remember? We were...{nl}
{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...huh??{nl}
Why are we even here?{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's see... I was having a{nl}
good dream... woke up, and{nl}
Tamaki was right there...{waitkey}{clearbox}and Tamaki was looking{nl}
at me too...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yes yes yes yes!!{nl}
I get it,{wait_fr:30} I get it!{nl}
Congrats! Spare us the rest!!{waitkey}{clearbox}More importantly, you two,{nl}
just tell me this one thing.{nl}
Then I won't bother you{waitkey}two anymore.{waitkey}{clearbox}So, does either of you{nl}
have a "Mirror Shard"?{waitkey}It's something very important.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hm. I expect nothing{nl}
from the start, but{nl}
for now.{waitkey}{clearbox}Does either of you have one?{nl}
A "Mirror Shard."{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: ...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
Nope!{waitkey}{clearbox}I've only got my hand{nl}
mirror for styling my hair.{nl}
Will this do?{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: ...Honestly!{nl}
Dummy Tadashi!{nl}
Of course not!{waitkey}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...!{waitkey}{clearbox}Is this the "Mirror Shard"{nl}
Mayuzumi means?{waitkey}{clearbox}It was in my pocket{nl}
before I knew it...{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: ...Ehh?!{nl}
Tamaki!!{nl}
Y-you had something{waitkey}like that...{waitkey}{clearbox}I didn't hear about it!!{nl}
Ahh! We pledged our love,{nl}
yet{wait_fr:30} yet{wait_fr:30} yet!{waitkey}{clearbox}Keeping a secret!!{nl}
So cruel, so cruel!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: ...Hey!{nl}
I only just noticed{nl}
it myself!{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't make me sound bad!{nl}
...Be quiet a moment!{waitkey}{clearbox}Here, if this will do,{nl}
take it,{nl}
{ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{clearbox}...Heehee. Remember I said{nl}
"next it's your turn"?{waitkey}{clearbox}That... really came true,{nl}
huh. But I'm sure you{nl}
can pull it off.{waitkey}{clearbox}Good luck!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: ...Hey!{nl}
I only just noticed{nl}
it myself!{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't make me sound bad!{nl}
...Be quiet a moment!{waitkey}{clearbox}Here, if this will do,{nl}
take it,{nl}
{ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{clearbox}Sorry I can only help{nl}
with something this small...{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly I wish Tadashi and{nl}
I could come along too,{waitkey}{clearbox}but as we are now, we'd{nl}
only be a burden to you.{waitkey}{clearbox}Thanks for saving us.{nl}
Good luck!{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Hmm,{nl}
I don't really get it, but{nl}
good luck out there!{waitkey}{clearbox}Leave Tamaki to me!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Yay!{nl}
Super lucky!!{nl}
"Mirror Shard" GET!{waitkey}{clearbox}Going all the way to the{nl}
Anti-Dream World paid off!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey hey!! If Tamaki and{nl}
Tadashi had a "Mirror Shard,"{nl}
then maybe{waitkey}{clearbox}Ms. Natsumi has one too??{nl}
Shall we ask her?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey hey, Ms. Natsumi!{nl}
You don't have a "Mirror{nl}
Shard"? Teach{wait_fr:30} teach{wait_fr:30} TEACH!{waitkey}{clearbox}The "Mirror Shard"?!{nl}
You're awake! Teacher!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: ...So noisy.{nl}
I've got low blood pressure...{nl}
owowow... my head hurts.{waitkey}{clearbox}So? A mi{wait_fr:30}rr{wait_fr:30}or...?{nl}
...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
Nope! ...Goodnight... zzz{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Tch.{nl}
Aw, teach doesn't have one.{nl}
Waking her was a waste!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Are those two still{nl}
half asleep? Well,{nl}
whatever.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: All right then,{nl}
shall we go take down{nl}
the boss now?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: They said Tadashi{nl}
sometimes goes totally{nl}
out of control,{waitkey}{clearbox}so this is what they meant.{nl}
Hmm, super passionate~{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Mmm, Ayase wants{nl}
a super hot relationship{nl}
like that with someone too!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Do they still intend{nl}
to stay in the Anti-Dream{nl}
World?{waitkey}{clearbox}Then I can't see why we{nl}
woke the two of them.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: We've wasted a good{nl}
deal of time.{nl}
No complaints now, surely.{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's hurry on.{nl}
Well...{wait_fr:30} all three being safe{nl}
wasn't a bad thing, I suppose.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Daaamn it!{nl}
Is Tamaki still half{nl}
asleep or what?{waitkey}{clearbox}Why pick that Tadashi guy{nl}
over the great me?{nl}
I've got my doubts!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Thanks to my big{nl}
heroics, all three are safe!{nl}
Wahahahahaha!!{waitkey}{clearbox}I've got just outstanding{nl}
leader material, I tell ya!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Surely Hypnos's magic{nl}
doesn't{wait_fr:30} still linger...{nl}
does it?{waitkey}{clearbox}Truly, I've had quite{nl}
an eyeful.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: By chance, Hypnos{nl}
ended up becoming{nl}
Tadashi and Tamaki's{waitkey}Cupid of love, it seems.{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Ahh! Ahh!{nl}
So annoying! Interrupting{nl}
someone's romance like this -{waitkey}{clearbox}what a rude person{nl}
you are! Save it for later!!{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: You're done with{nl}
your business, right? Leave{nl}
us alone, would you, please?{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: You mean to get in{nl}
the way of me and Tadashi?{nl}
I won't forgive you!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Sorry, but right now{nl}
I can't think of anything{nl}
but Tadashi.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Zzz{wait_fr:30}...zpii{nl}
...heehee...{wait_fr:30}well?...{nl}
...is it{wait_fr:30}...tasty?...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Ngghh!!{nl}
I'm wide awake now, but my{nl}
head's killing me.{waitkey}{clearbox}The dream was nice, though...{nl}
Feels like I got interrupted{nl}
at a really good part...{waitkey}{ret}
